{"type": "article", "id": 13163, "title": "多功能水杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-07T07:28:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000253aWQe1jKzb7ZMfrnv.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t视频设计网站 MOLD 和布鲁克林设计工作室内 Visibility 合作推出了一个大的“量杯”，它是一个设计非常简单的玻璃杯，杯壁上被套了不同颜色的硅胶圈，你可以调整硅胶圈的位置来满足不同情形下对于水量的需求，浇花，喝茶，或者单纯的喝水，都是一个简单而实用的工具。不过，是不是看起来蛮像矿泉水瓶套了个橡胶圈。（走开，当然不一样啦！）这是<a href=\"https://thisismold.com/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140810HkUpqSP1ahbF6BWK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140811M8gnErck73Rfjxs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140811kimO08s7AD13naRT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614081278bGZFd49qOHR1rD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140812rbHC3RjYg8e7X1VT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140813p9JUObEW8eudgfHR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140814VWjGl4mXCI3pL7qg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140814U1ubpmNShHOITwV2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n\n\n\n"}